<https://tetherless-world.github.io/idea-ontology/ontology#Evaluation> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#seeAlso> "https://www.sfu.ca/rst/05bibliographies/bibs/ISI_RS_87_190.pdf" .
